WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Seashell fractions are all around us!

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:08.000
When shells break into pieces, we can learn about parts and wholes.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Half a shell, quarter pieces - fractions help us describe what we see.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Each broken shell tells a story of ocean mathematics.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Let's piece together our understanding of fractions!